to take the shots in the middle of his back.

--- RoboRick007 <rfa007@...> wrote:
> ::Kup::
> 
> "That's fine. We'll discuss the energon later. Right
> now, we got a Pred to kill."
> 
> Kup pulled his blaster from subspace and backed
> Sunhawk.
> 
> Kup fired three good laser shots at Megatron.
> 
> ::Hot Rod::
> 
> He heard the comm message.
> 
> "Ok, be good, Arcee. I'll see you when we're done
> kicking Megatron's tail across the planet!"
> 
> Hot Rod quickly left, running out of the base, and
> transforming to car mode. He headed for the battle
> at maximum speed.
>
